    "body": "@rafajaques That menu only appears when a window of your application has focus.  You could technically trick OS X into thinking your window was in focus by making a frameless, transparent 1x1 window when you want that menu to appear.  But that is both hacky and bad practice.\n\nUp to you though :laughing: \n"
